    "locked": false,
    "maintainer_can_modify": false,
    "title": "net: prevent signed integer overflow in AddLocal nScore update",
    "user": {
      "login": "chriszeng1010",
      "id": 166641110,
      "node_id": "U_kgDOCe691g",
      "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/166641110?v=4",
      "gravatar_id": "",
      "url": "https://api.github.com/users/chriszeng1010",
      "html_url": "https://github.com/chriszeng1010",
      "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/chriszeng1010/followers",
      "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/chriszeng1010/following%7B/other_user%7D",
      "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/chriszeng1010/gists%7B/gist_id%7D",
      "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/chriszeng1010/starred%7B/owner%7D%7B/repo%7D",
      "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/chriszeng1010/subscriptions",
      "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/chriszeng1010/orgs",
      "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/chriszeng1010/repos",
      "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/chriszeng1010/events%7B/privacy%7D",
      "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/chriszeng1010/received_events",
      "type": "User",
      "site_admin": false,
      "name": null,
      "patch_url": null
    },
    "body": "When `AddLocal()` is called for an address already in mapLocalHost, it increments nScore by 1. If nScore is at INT_MAX, this is signed integer overflow (undefined behavior).\r\n\r\nUse `SaturatingAdd `from` util/overflow.h` to cap at INT_MAX instead.\r\n\r\nThis is the same class of bug addressed for `SeenLocal()` in #[34028](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/34028/changes/3fc5948e1feeb13babeeb7c4e32c97dc35f630d5), but in a different call site.\r\n",
    "labels": [
      {
        "id": 98298007,
        "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWw5ODI5ODAwNw==",
